response.original_title: PAW Patrol: Splash To The Rescue
response.overview: Splash into action with the PAW Patrol in these 8 wave-making adventures. First, the pups head to the beach to rescue Grandma Tilly. Then, a super-strong wind sweeps up all the surfers in the Adventure Bay Windsurfing Race! There's so much to see, from a giant Sea Slug to a manatee as the PAW Patrol dives to the rescue!  Pups Save Tilly Turbot  Merpups Save the Turbots  Pups Save a Duck Pond  Pups Save the Diving Bell  Pups Save a Windy Bay  Pups Save a Chicken of the Sea  Pups Save a Manatee  Pups Save a Freighter
response.title: PAW Patrol: Splash To The Rescue
